a:2:{s:7:"content";s:6411:"<h1 class="text-center">Step 10 - How to add Information Zones</h1>
<p>You can also call it a Chat / Dialog as you can tell a whole Story with this.</p>
<p>First of all, you have to create the actual chat in the <code>src/consts/DB_SEED/Chats.js</code></p>
<p>This is the Structure of the object:</p>
<pre><code>export const CHATS = [
    ..., // Other code
    {
        id: 2,
